               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols. 2ra-104vb) &#xD;
I-1) Homily by Timothy (Damātewos), Patriarch of Alexandria for the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 2ra-7vb); miracle (fols. 8ra-10rb); commemorative notice (fols. 10rb-11vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 11vb-12rb) &#xD;
I-2) Homily by an anonymous author for Tāḫśāś (fols. 12rb-17vb); miracle (fols. 17vb-19rb); commemorative notice (fols. 19rb-20ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 20ra-rb) &#xD;
I-3) Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for Ṭǝrr (fols. 20ra-29ra); miracle (fol. 29ra-vb); commemorative notice (fol. 30ra-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 30vb) &#xD;
I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for Yakkātit (fols. 31ra-34ra); miracle (fols. 34ra-35ra); commemorative notice (fol. 35ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 35ra-rb) &#xD;
I-5) Homily by [Severus] Patriarch of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 35va-51ra); miracle (fols. 51rb-52rb); commemorative notice (fol. 52rb-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 52va-vb) &#xD;
I-6) Homily by [Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] the Orthodox for Miyāzyā (fols. 53ra-57rb); miracle (fols. 57rb -58va); commemorative notice (fol. 58va-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 58vb-59rb) &#xD;
I-7) Homily by Patriarch Yoḥannǝs ʾAfa Warq [Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia] for the 12th of Gǝnbot (fols. 59va-65ra); miracle (fols. 65ra-66vb); commemorative notice (fols. 66vb-67rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 67rb) &#xD;
I-8) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, ʾeṗisqoṗos [Metropolitan] of ʾAksum for Sane (fols. 68ra-73vb); miracle (fols. 73vb-75ra); commemorative notice (fols. 75ra-81vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 81vb-82rb) &#xD;
I-9) Homily [by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for Ḥamle (fols. 82va-86vb); miracle (fol. 87ra-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 87vb-88rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 88rb-vb) &#xD;
I-10) Homily by an anonymous author for Naḥāse (fols. 89ra-92ra); miracle (fol. 92ra-va); commemorative notice (fols. 92vb-93ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 93ra-rb) &#xD;
I-11) Homily by an anonymous author for Maskaram (fols. 93va-96ra); miracle (fol. 96rb-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 96vb-97rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 97rb) &#xD;
I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 97va-101vb); miracle (fols. 101vb-104ra); commemorative notice (fol. 104ra-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 104vb) &#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-4.</summary>
